# PlatForge Environment Configuration

# Service account NPSSO token for public mode (optional)
# When set, users can search PSN profiles without providing their own NPSSO token.
# Without this, users must connect their own PSN account via the UI.
#
# How to get:
# 1. Log into https://store.playstation.com/ with your service PSN account
# 2. Visit https://ca.account.sony.com/api/v1/ssocookie
# 3. Copy the npsso value from the JSON response
#
# The token bootstraps access/refresh tokens that auto-renew.
# If the refresh chain breaks (extended downtime, Sony invalidation), get a new token.
SERVICE_NPSSO=

# Server port (default: 3001)
# PORT=3001
